entries.description: Britain, France, and Germany plan to censure Iran at the UN nuclear watchdog's Vienna meeting despite US opposition, over Tehran's lack of cooperation in enriching uranium to 60% and accumulating large stockpiles, nearing levels for atomic weapons.
